title: Lipyantara
abstract: >-
  A personal, offline-first Sanskrit script converter for Devanagari, IAST,
  Harvard-Kyoto, ITRANS, and Velthuis, powered by the Aksharamukha
  transliteration engine running client-side via WebAssembly.
